title: Railworks TS2015 BR 6MT Clan Class
description:
The 6MT Clan Class for Train Simulator is a former Iron Horse House model, which has been updated to TS2015 standard, including new scenarios and improved exterior modelling. It is available in BR Brunswick Green livery with BR Mk1 passenger and sleeper coaches in maroon livery. 

The locomotive is also Quick Drive compatible, giving you the freedom to drive the BR 6MT Clan Class on any Quick Drive enabled route for Train Simulator. Also included are scenarios specifically for the Western Lines of Scotland route (available separately and required to play these scenarios).




Please support the developers and buy some of their content if you can afford it.


If you would like to contribute, please read the Readme.pdf.
